    <body><p><seg rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
玄道先生唯今御入来相成候、<seg type="ruby"><seg type="rb">依而</seg><seg type="rp">（</seg><seg type="rt">（よつて）</seg><seg type="rp">）</seg></seg>雅兄早<seg facs="../../../gaiji/1-02/1-02-22.png" rend="gaiji" rendition="img" source="※(二の字点、1-2-22)" />御出<seg type="ruby"><seg type="rb">被<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</seg>下</seg><seg type="rp">（</seg><seg type="rt">（くだされ）</seg><seg type="rp">）</seg></seg>ず候てハ、天下の<seg type="ruby"><seg type="rb">儀</seg><seg type="rp">（</seg><seg type="rt">（ママ）</seg><seg type="rp">）</seg></seg>論<seg type="ruby"><seg type="rb">初</seg><seg type="rp">（</seg><seg type="rt">（はじま）</seg><seg type="rp">）</seg></seg>りかね申候。<lb />
何卒御足おすゝめさせたまへと申すハ<lb />
<seg rend="jisage_2" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 2em">十六日<seg rend="chitsuki_0" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 0em">龍馬</seg></seg>
<lb />
　伊藤先生<seg rend="chitsuki_0" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 0em">坂本</seg>
<seg rend="jisage_5" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 5em">足下</seg>
